text: Dino Kluk (born 13 May 1991) is a professional Croatian football player, who plays for NK Zagorec Krapina. ==Career== He previously played for FK Dukla Prague in the Czech First League.. Retrieved 1 November 2014. He left Dukla in August 2015.
